    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《发现像素异常》游戏中，你的任务是监控实时监控摄像头的画面。识别监控区域内的任何异常情况。这些异常可能包括家具缺失，甚至是可爱的访客。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290400/extras/2d9c10cbba6434d6c89edf3079effadf.poster.avif?t=1772142063\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290400/extras/2d9c10cbba6434d6c89edf3079effadf.webm?t=1772142063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290400/extras/2d9c10cbba6434d6c89edf3079effadf.mp4?t=1772142063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现异常了吗？提交报告，并希望它能及时修复。否则你会遇到麻烦，因为过多的异常将导致游戏结束。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290400/extras/f5d951c05db82439fd9c2acf24ae5020.avif?t=1772142063\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290400/extras_big/f5d951c05db82439fd9c2acf24ae5020.avif?t=1772142063 width=800 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开启夜视模式，揭示潜伏在阴影中的最难发现的异常。但不要太放松——这个模式限制了你能看到的内容，每一个错误都可能是致命的。专注于隐藏的细节，在它们结束你的游戏之前发现威胁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290400/extras/ed93c16889e7d91d56ec47de22239e1f.avif?t=1772142063\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290400/extras_big/ed93c16889e7d91d56ec47de22239e1f.avif?t=1772142063 width=800 height=86 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多余物品</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >等下，这张椅子之前在这里吗？是谁放的？不管怎样，你最好快点提交报告。这些新增的物品很容易融入环境，所以保持警惕。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>入侵者</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >它们看起来可能很可爱，但别被迷惑，这些生物可不怀好意。它们伪装技术高超，所以多加留意。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>图像</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一张图片胜过千言万语，但一千个词也救不了你。仔细观察画作、标志和海报中的任何不安的变化，它们可能是异常的信号。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>物品丢失</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是有东西不见了吗，还是你疑神疑鬼？只要有东西“消失”了，就提交报告。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290400/extras/027cd5ff8d70d5a2336923bdd1ac94c5.poster.avif?t=1772142063\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290400/extras/027cd5ff8d70d5a2336923bdd1ac94c5.webm?t=1772142063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290400/extras/027cd5ff8d70d5a2336923bdd1ac94c5.mp4?t=1772142063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>还有更多异常类型</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但没有什么比一个小秘密更令人期待。你能找到它们全部吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290400/extras/9503f17c27da43feb23e7dbfd8a6a5b3.avif?t=1772142063\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290400/extras_big/9503f17c27da43feb23e7dbfd8a6a5b3.avif?t=1772142063 width=800 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在四张地图中，有近100个异常等待你发现，每个地点都带来了独特的挑战和谜题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >博物馆</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >商场</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >??? (敬请期待)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >??? (敬请期待)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每张地图包含多达20种独特的异常和3种重复出现的异常。每次游戏都是独特的，因为异常是随机分布的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290400/extras/ae12fd308b654d87f65bef953a2ad1c8.avif?t=1772142063\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290400/extras_big/ae12fd308b654d87f65bef953a2ad1c8.avif?t=1772142063 width=800 height=86 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你准备好发现每一个异常了吗？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《发现像素异常》结合了舒适的视觉效果和微妙的悬念，是一款将在最意想不到的方式上考验你注意力的游戏。每次游戏都是一个全新的挑战。你能在夜晚不漏掉任何细节吗？</p>",
